/***********************************************
 * Introduction
 ***********************************************/
 NVPipe is a H.264-based lightweight library for image compression. 
 It provides access to hardware accelerated NVIDIA Video Codec as well
 as software fallbak libx264. 

/***********************************************
 * Build
 ***********************************************/
 Requires FFmpeg library built with NVENC / CUVID / CUDA / libx264 

    [
        cmake /PATH_TO_CORE
        make
        make install
    ]

/***********************************************
 * Usage
 ***********************************************/
 Please refer to nvpipe.h for instructions.
